hadiths[123]{hadithnumber,text}:
2736,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' eik musalman key doosrey musalman par husne-suluk key chhe umoomi huquq hain : (1) jab us sey mulaqat ho to usey salam karey. (2) jab wo dawat dey to uski dawat ko qubul karey. (3) jab usey chheenk aaye (aur wo « الحمد لله » kahey ( to « يرحمك الله » keh kar uski chheenk ka jawab dey. (4) jab wo bimar pad jaey to uski iyaadat karey. (5) jab wo mar jaey to uskey janaazey key sath (qabristaan) jaey. (6) aur uskey liye wohi pasand karey jo apney liye pasand karta ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees mutaaddid (bahut si) sanadon sey Nabi karim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai. 3- baaz muhaddeseen ney Haris aa'war sey mutalliq kalam kiya hai. 4- aur is baab mein Abu-Hurera , abu-Ayyub , Bara aur ibne-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2737,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin key momin par chhe huquq hain : (1) jab bimar ho to uski bimar pursi karey. (2) jab marey to uskey janaazey mein shareek ho. (3) jab dawat karey to qubul karey. (4) jab miley to usey salam karey. (5) jab usey chheenk aaye to uski chheenk ka jawab dey. (6) uskey samney mojud rahey ya na rahey uska khair-khawah ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Muhammad bin Musa Makhzoomi Madni Suqa (bharosemand) hain un sey Abdul-Azeez ibne Muhammad aur ibne-Abi Fidya ney riwayat ki hai.
2738,"ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key pehlu mein bethey huye eik shakhs ko chheenk aai to usney kaha (الحمدللہ والسلام Ali رسول اللہ) yani tamam tareef Allah key liye hai aur salam hai Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par. ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : kehney ko to main bhi (الحمدللہ والسلام Ali رسول اللہ) keh sakta hun padhi. lekin is tarah kehna Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein nahin sikhlaya hai. aap ney hamen bataya hai ke hum (الحمد لله على كل حال) har haal mein sab taarifein Allah hi key liye hain, kahen. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Ziyad bin Rabee ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2739,"Yahud Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas hotey to ye ummid laga kar chhenkte ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unkey liye « يرحمكم الله » ''Allah tum par reham karey'' kahin gey. magar aap (us moqe par sirf) « يهديكم الله ويصلح بالكم » ''Allah tumhen hidayat dey aur tumhara haal durust kar dey'' farmatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , abu-Ayyub , Salim bin Ubaid , Abdullah bin Jaafar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2740,"wo logon key sath eik safar mein they, un mein sey eik shakhs ko chheenk aai to usney kaha : «السلام عليكم» (iskey jawab mein) Salim (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : « عليك وعلى وأمك » (salam hai tum par aur tumhari maa par), ye baat us shakhs ko nagawar malum hui to Salim ney kaha : Bhai ! mainey to wohi kaha hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kaha hai. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik shakhs ko chheenk aai to usney kaha « السلام عليكم » to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kaha : 'عليك وعلى أمك , (tum par aur tumhari maa par bhi salamti ho). (aap ney aagey farmaya ( jab tum mein sey kisi shakhs ko chheenk aaye to usey (الحمدللہ رب العالمین) kehna chahiye. aur jawab deney wala (یرحمک اللہ) aur ( chheenkney wala ( « يغفر الله لي ولكم » kahey , (na ke « السلام عليك » kahey). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye eik aisi hadees hai jis mein Mansoor sey riwayat karney mein logon ney ikhtilaf kiya hai, logon ney Hilal bin Yasaaf aur Salim key darmiyan eik aur Raavi ko dakhil kiya hai."
2741,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab kisi ko chheenk aaye to (الحمد لله على كل حال) ( tamam tareefen har haal mein Allah key liye hain ( kahey. aur jo uska jawab dey wo « يرحمك الله » kahey, aur uskey jawab mein chheenkney wala kahey « يهديكم الله ويصلح بالكم » ( Allah tumhen hidayat dey aur tumhari haalat durust farma dey)."
2742,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas do aadmiyon ko chheenk aai , aap ney eik ki chheenk par « يرحمك الله » keh kar dua di aur doosrey ki chheenk ka aap ney jawab nahin diya, to jiski chheenk ka aap ney jawab na diya tha usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney uski chheenk par (يرحمك الله) keh kar dua di aur meri chheenk par aap ney mujhey ye dua nahin di? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(chheenk aai to) usney Allah ki hamd bayan ki aur (tujhey chheenk aai to) tum ney uski hamd na ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai."
2743,meri mojudgi mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik shakhs ko chheenk aai to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : « يرحمك الله » ( Allah tum par reham farmaai ( phir usey dobara chheenk aai to aap ney farmaya : ''isey to zukaam ho gaya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2744,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''chheenkney waley ki chheenk ka jawab teen baar diya jaeyga, aur agar teen baar sey ziyada chheenke ayen to tumhen ikhtiyar hai ji chahey to jawab do aur ji chahey to na do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai aur iski sanad majhool (anjaan) hai."
2745,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko jab chheenk aati thi to apney haath sey ya apney kapdey sey munh dhanp letey, aur apni aawaz ko dheemi kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2746,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''chhinknaa Allah ki janib sey hai aur jamaai shetan ki janib sey hai. jab kisi ko jamaai aaye to usey chahiye ke jamaai aatey waqt apna haath munh par rakh ley , aur jab jamaai leney wala aah , aah karta hai to shetan jamaai leney waley key pet mein ghus kar hanstaa hai. aur beshak Allah chheenk ko pasand karta hai aur jamaai leney ko napasand karta hai. to (jaan lo) ke aadmi jab jamaai key waqt aah aah ki aawaz nikalta hai to us waqt shetan uskey pet key andar ghus kar hanstaa hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2747,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala chheenk ko pasand karta hai aur jamaai ko napasand , pas (isliye) jab tum mein sey kisi ko chheenk aaye aur wo (Alhamdulillah) kahey to har musalman key liye jo usey suney (یرحمک اللہ) kehna zaruri hai. ab rahi jamaai ki baat to jis kisi ko jamaai aaye , usey chahiye ke wo apni taqat bhar usey rokey aur ha ha na kahey, kyonkey ye shetan ki taraf sey hai, aur shetan us sey hanstaa hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- aur ye ibne Ajlan ki (oopper mazkur) riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai. 3- ibne-Abi Zi-ib : Saeed Maqbari ki hadees ko ziyada yad rakhney waley aur Muhammad bin Ajlan sey ziyada qawi hain. 4- mainey abu-Bakar Attaar Basraa sey suna hai wo riwayat kartey hain : Ali bin Madini key wastey sey Yahya bin Saeed sey aur Yahya bin Saeed kehtey hain : Muhammad bin Ajlan kehtey hain : Saeed Maqbari ki ahadees ka maamla ye hai ke Saeed ney baaz hadisein (bilaa-waasta) Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki hain. aur baaz hadisein ba-wasta eik shakhs key Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki gaee hain. to wo sab merey zehen mein gadmad ho gaeen. mujhey yad nahin raha ke bilaa-waasta kon thin aur ba-wasta kon? to mainey sabhi riwaayaton ko Saeed key wastey sey Abu-Hurera sey riwayat kar di hai."
2748,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''namaz mein chheenk , ungh , jamaai , haiz , qai aur Nakseer shetan ki taraf sey hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Shareek ki riwayat se jantey hain jisey wo Abul Yaqzaan sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is riwayat (عن عدی بن ثابت an ابیہ an جدہ) key talluq sey puchha ke Adi key dada ka kya naam hai? to unhoney kaha ke main nahin janta , lekin Yahya bin Moayan sey puchha gaya to unhoney kaha ke unka naam Dinar hai."
2749,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi shakhs apney bhai ko uskey bethney ki jagah sey utha kar khud uski jagah na beth jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2750,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey koi shakhs apney bhai ko uski jagah sey utha kar khud us jagah na beth jaey.'' Raavi Salim kehtey hain : ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key ehtiraam mein aadmi unkey aaney par apni jagah sey uth kar khada ho jata tha lekin wo (is mumaaniat ki wajeh sey) uski jagah nahin bethtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai. aur phir wapis aaye to wo apni jagah par bethney ka ziyada mustahiq hai.
2751,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi apney bethney ki jagah ka ziyada mustahiq hai, agar wo kisi zarurat sey uth kar jaey aur phir wapis aaye to wohi apni jagah par bethney ka ziyada haq rakhta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakra , abu Saeed Khudri aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hai."
2752,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kisi bhi shakhs key liye jayez nahin ke wo do aadmiyon key bich mein beth kar tafriq (farq) paida karey magar un ki ijazat sey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees ko Aamir Ahwal ney Amr bin Shuaib sey bhi riwayat ki hai.
2753,"eik aadmi halqe key beech mein beth gaya, to Huzefa ney kaha : Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key farman key mutabiq wo shakhs maloon hai jo bethey huye logon key halqe (daayre) key beech mein ja kar bethey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- abu-Mujliz ka naam Laahiq bin Humeed hai."
2754,koi shakhs unhen yani ( Sahaba ( ko Rasoolullah sey ziyada mehbub na tha kehtey hain : (lekin) wo log aap ko dekh kar (adaban) khadey na hotey they. isliye ke wo log jantey they ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam isey napasand kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai.
2755,"Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bahar nikley , Abdullah bin Zuber aur ibne Safwan unhen dekh kar (eahatraman) khadey ho gaey. to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha tum dono beth jaao. mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : ''jo shakhs ye pasand karey ke log uskey samney baa adab khadey hon to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Umama sey bhi riwayat hai, hum sey bayan kiya Hannaad ney wo kehtey hain : hum sey bayan kiya abu-Usaama ney aur abu-Usaama ney Habib bin Shaheed sey Habib bin Shaheed ney abu-Mujliz sey abu-Mujliz ney Muawiya key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki."
2756,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''paanch cheezen fitrat sey hain : (1) sharmgaah key baal moondnaa. (2) khatna karna. (3) munchhein kutarnaa. (4) baghal key baal ukhednaa. (5) nakhun taraashnaa.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2757,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''das padhi. cheezen fitrat sey hain :(1) munchhein kutarnaa. (2) dadhhi badhaanaa. (3) miswak karna. (4) naak mein pani dalna. (5) nakhun kaatnaa. (6) ungliyon key jodon ki pusht dhonaa. (7) baghal key baal ukhednaa. (8) naaf sey nichey key baal moondnaa. (9) pani sey istinja karna. Zakariya (Raavi) kehtey hain ke Musab ney kaha : daswin chiz mein bhool gaya. ho sakta hai ke wo kulli karna ho.''  « انتقاص الماء » sey murad pani sey istinja karna hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Ammar bin Yasir , ibne-Umar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2758,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon key liye muddat mutayyan farma di hai ke har chaalis din key andar nakhun kaat lein. munchhein katarwa lein. aur naaf sey nichey key baal moond lein.
2759,"munchhein katarney , nakhun kaatney, zere-naaf key baal leney , aur baghal key baal ukhaadney ka hamarey liye waqt muqarrar farma diya gaya hai, aur wo ye hai ke hum unhen chaalis din sey ziyada na chhodey rakhen. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, 2- sadqa bin Musa (jo pehli hadees ki sanad mein) muhaddeseen key nazdik Hafiz nahin hain."
2760,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni munchhein kaat'tey they. aur farmatey they ke khaleelur-Rehman Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) bhi aisa hi kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2761,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney apni moonchhon key baal na liye (yani unhen nahin kaata) to wo hum mein sey nahin hai ''.
2762,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni daadhi lambaai aur chorai sey liya kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey huye suna hai : umr bin Harun maqaribul-Hadees hain. main unki koi aisi hadees nahin janta jiski asal na ho, ya ye ke main koi aisi hadees nahin janta jis mein wo munfarid hon, siwaye is hadees key ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni daadhi ki lambai tool o arz sey kuch letey they. mein usey sirf umr bin Harun ki riwayat sey janta hun. mainey unhen (yani Bukhari ko umr bin Harun) key barey mein achi raey rakhney wala paya hai, 3- mainey Quteba ko umr bin Harun key barey mein kehtey huye suna hai ke umr bin Harun sahab hadees they. aur wo kehtey they ke eman qol o amal ka naam hai, 4- Quteba ney kaha : Wakee bin Jarrah ney mujh sey eik shakhs key wastey sey Sor bin Yazeed sey bayan kya Sor bin Yazeed sey aur soor bin Yazeed riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ehale-taaif par minjneeq nasb kar diya. Quteba kehtey hain mainey (apney ustaad) Wakee bin Jarrah sey puchha ke ye shakhs kon hain? (jinka aap ney abhi riwayat mein (عن رجل) keh kar zikr kya hai) to unhoney kaha : ye tumharey sathi umr bin Harun hain."
2763,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' munchhein kaato aur daadhiyaan badhaao''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai.
2764,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen munchhein katwaaney aur dadhiyan badhaaney ka hukm diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key azad karda ghulam abu-Bakar bin Nafey Suqa aadmi hain, 3- umr bin Nafey ye bhi Suqa hain, 4- Abdullah bin Nafey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key azad karda ghulam hain aur hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain."
2765,unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko masjid main apni eik taang dusri taang par rakh kar chit letey huye dekha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2766,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi apni peeth key bal letey to apni eik taang dusri taang par na rakhey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko kaee raawiyon ney Suleman (Alaihissalam) Taimi sey riwayat kya hai. aur Khaddash (jinka zikr is hadees ki sanad mein hai) nahin janey jatey ke wo kon hain? aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) Taimi ney un sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain.
2767,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik kapdey mein Sammaa aur Ehtibaa karney aur eik taang dusri taang par rakh kar chit letney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2768,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik shakhs ko apney pet key bal ( ondhey munh ( letaa huwa dekha to farmaya : '' ye aisa letna hai jisey Allah pasand nahin karta''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Yahya bin abi Kasir ney abu-Salma sey riwayat ki hai aur abu-Salma ney Yaeesh bin Tihfa key wastey sey unkey baap Tihfa sey riwayat ki hai, unhen Tikhfa bhi kaha jata hai, lekin sahih Tihfa hi hai. aur baaz Hafiz kehtey hain : Tikhfa sahih hai. aur unhen Tighfa aur Yaeesh bhi kaha jata hai. aur wo Sahaba mein sey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Tihfa aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2769,"mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool! hum apni Sharmgaahein kis qadr khol saktey aur kis qadr chupana zaruri hain? aap ney farmaya : ''apni biwi aur apni laundi key siwa har kisi sey apni sharmgaah ko chhipao'', unhoney kaha : aadmi kabhi aadmi key sath mil jal kar rehta hai? aap ney farmaya : ''tab bhi tumhari har mumkin koshish yehi honi chahiye ke tumhari sharmgaah koi na dekh sakey'', mainey kaha : aadmi kabhi tanha hota hai? aap ney farmaya : ''Allah to aur ziyada mustahiq hai ke us sey sharam ki jaey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Behaz key dada ka naam Muawiya bin Heda al-Qusheri hai. 3- aur Jareeri ney Hakim bin Muawiya sey riwayat ki hai aur wo Behaz key walid hain."
2770,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko apni baain janib takiyey par tek laga kar bethey huye dekha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko kaee aur ney b-tareeq : (إسرائيل an سماك an جابر بن سمرة) riwayat ki hai, (us mein hai) wo kehtey hain : mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko takiya par tek lagaey huye dekha , lekin unhoney (علی یسارہ) apni baain janib takiya rakhney ka zikr nahin kya."
2771,mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko takiya par tek lagaey huye dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai.
2772,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kisi key hudood iqtidar o ikhtiyar mein uski ijazat key baghair imaamat nahin karaaii ja sakti, aur na hi kisi shakhs key ghar mein uski khas jagah par uski ijazat key baghair betha ja sakta hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2773,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam chaley ja rahey they ke usi doran eik shakhs jis key sath gadha tha aap key paas aaya, aur aap sey arz kya : Allah key Rasool! aap sawar ho jaiye, aur khud peechey hat gaya. to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' to apni sawari key seeney par yani aagey bethney ka ziyada haqdaar ho siwaey ye ke tum mujhey uska haq dey do. ye sun kar fauran usney kaha : mainey uska haq aap ko dey diya.'' phir aap is par sawar ho gaey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is sanad sey ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. is baab mein Qais bin Saad bin Ubada sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2774,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya tumharey paas ghaalichey hain? ''main ney kaha : ghaalichey hamarey paas kahan sey hongey? aap ney farmaya : '' tumharey paas anqarib ghaalichey hongey ''. ( to ab wo zamana aa gaya hai) main apni biwi sey kehta hun ke tum apney ghaalichey mujh sey door rakho. to wo kehti hai : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye na kaha tha ke tumharey paas ghaalichey hongey, to main us sey darguzar kar jata hun''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2775,"mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Shehba naami khachar ko jis par aap, aur Hasan o Husain sawar they. aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key hujra key paas ( sehan mein) leta chala gaya, ye ( Hasan (aap key aagey aur wo (Husain) aapkey peechey bethey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- is mein ibne-Abbas aur Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2776,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey (kisi ajnabiya aurat par) achcha pad janey wali nazar sey mutalliq puchha . to aap ney farmaya : '' tum apni nigah pher liya karo'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2777,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Ali ! nazar key baad nazar na uthaao, kyonkey tumharey liye pehli nazar ( maaf ( hai aur dusri ( maaf ( nahin hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf shareek ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2778,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas thin aur Memuna (Raziallahu Anha) bhi mojud thin, usi doran ke hum dono aap key paas bethi thin, Abdullah bin Umme maktoom aaye aur aap key paas pahunch gaey . ye us waqt ki baat hai ke jab hamen pardey ka hukm diya ja chuka tha. to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum dono un sey parda karo '' , mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! kya wo andhey nahin hain? na wo hamen dekh saktey hain? aur na hamen pehchan saktey hain? to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya tum dono bhi andhi ho? kya tum dono unhen dekhti nahin ho?''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2779,"Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ( un ki biwi ( Asma binte-Umes padhi. sey mulaqat ki ijazat maangney key liye bheja, to unhoney ijazat dey di, phir jab wo jis zarurat sey gaey they us sey keh sun kar farigh huye to unkey Mola ( azad karda ghulam ( ney un sey) uskey mutalliq puchha , to unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen aurton key paas unkey shohron sey ijazat liye baghair janey sey mana farmaya hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aqba bin Aamir , Abdullah bin Amr aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2780,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mainey apney baad mardon key liye aurton sey ziyada nuqsan pahunchane-wala koi fitna nahin chhoda '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees kaee Suqa logon ney b-tareeq :  سليمان التيمي an أبي عثمان an أسامة بن زيد an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم sey riwayat ki hai. aur unhoney is sanad mein عن سعيد بن زيد بن عمرو بن نفيل ka zikr nahin kya, padhi. - hum moa'tamir key ilawa kisi ko nahin jantey jisney عن أسامة بن زيد وسعيد بن زيد ( eik sath ( kaha ho, 4- is bab mein abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2781,"mainey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko Madina mein khutbey key doran kehtey huye suna : aey ehle-Madina! tumharey ulama kahan hain? mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko un zayed baalon key istimal sey mana kartey huye suna hai aur aap kehtey they : '' jab Bani-Israel ki aurton ney isey apna liya to wo halak ho gaey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees bahut-si sanadon sey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki gaee hai."
2782,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney lanat farmaai hai godna godney wali aur godna gudwaaney waaliyon par aur husn mein izaafey ki khatir chehrey sey baal ukhaadney wali aur ukhedwaney waaliyon par aur Allah ki banawat (takhleeq) mein tabdilyan karney waaliyon par. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is hadees ko Shoba aur kaee doosrey aimma ney bhi mansoor sey riwayat kya hai."
2783,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ki lanat ho baalon ko jodney wali aur judwaane wali par aur godna godney aur godna gudwaane wali par.''  Nafey kehtey hain : gudaae masudhe mein hoti hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Maaqil bin Yasaar, Asma binte Abi Bakr aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. hum sey Muhammad bin Bashaar ney bayan kiya, wo kehtey hain : hum sey Yahya bin Saeed ney wo kehtey hain : hum sey Ubedullah bin umr ney Nafey sey aur Nafey ney ibne-Umar key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi (mazkoora) riwayat ki tarah riwayat ki. magar Yahya ney is riwayat mein Nafey ka qol zikr nahin kiya."
2784,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney lanat farmaae hai un aurton par jo mardon sey mushaabihat (hamshakli) ikhtiyar karti hain aur un mardon par jo aurton sey mushaabihat ikhtiyar kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2785,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney lanat farmaee zananey (mukhannas) mardon par, aur mardaana-pan ikhtiyar karney wali aurton par. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2786,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har aankh zina kaar hai aur aurat jab khushbu laga kar majlis key paas sey guzrey to wo bhi aisi aisi hai yani wo bhi zaaniya hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2787,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mardon ki khushbu wo hai jiski mehak phel rahi ho aur rang chhupa huwa ho aur aurton ki khushbu wo hai jis ka rang zahir ho lekin mehak uski chhupi hui ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2788,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : ''mard ki behtareen khushbu wo hai jiski mehak pheley aur uska rang chhupa rahey, aur aurton ki behtareen khushbu wo hai jis ka rang zahir ho aur khushbu chhupi rahey.''  aur aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney zeen key ooper intehai surkh reshmi kapda dalney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
2789,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) khushbu (ki chiz) wapis nahin kartey they, aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khushbu ko wapis na kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2790,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''teen cheezen (hadiye aur tohfe mein aaeen) to wo wapis nahin ki jati hain : takiye, dahan, aur doodh, dahan (tel) sey murad khushbu hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Abdullah ye Muslim bin Jundub key betey hain aur Madni hain."
2791,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey kisi ko khushbu di jaey to wo usey wapis na karey kyonkey wo jannat sey nikli hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Hanan (naam key) Raavi ko hum sirf isi hadees mein paatey hain. 3- abu-Usman Nahdi ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin Mil hai, unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka zamana to paya lekin unhen aap ka deedar nasib na huwa aur na hi aap sey koi hadees sun sakey."
2792,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aurat aurat sey na chimte yahan tak ke wo usey apney shohar sey is tarah bayan karey goya wo isey dekh raha hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2793,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mard mard ki sharmgaah aur aurat aurat ki sharmgaah ki taraf na dekhey, aur mard mard key sath eik kapdey mein nanga ho kar na letey aur aurat aurat key sath eik kapdey mein na letey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan , gharib sahih hai."
2794,mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! hum apni sharmgahe kis qadr khol saktey hain aur kis qadr chhupana zaruri? aap ney farmaya : ''tum apni sharmgaah apni biwi aur apni laundi key siwa har eik sey chhupaao.'' mainey phir kaha : jab log mil jul-kar reh rahey hon (to hum kya aur kaisey karen?) aap ney farmaya : ''tab bhi tumhari har mumkin koshish yehi honi chahiye ke tumhari sharmgaah koi na dekh sakey.''  mainey phir kaha : Allah key Nabi ! jab aadmi tanha ho? aap ney farmaya : ''logon key muqabil Allah to aur ziyada mustahiq hai ke us sey sharam ki jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2795,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam masjid mein Jarhad key paas (yani merey paas sey) sey guzrey (us waqt) un ki raan khuli hui thi to aap ney farmaya : ''raan bhi sattar (chhipaaney ki chiz) hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- merey nazdik iski sanad muttasil nahin hai.
2796,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unkey paas sey guzrey aur wo apni raan kholey huye they to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''apni raan dhanp lo kyonkey ye sattar (chhipaaney ki chiz) hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2797,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''raan sattar (chhipaaney ki chiz) hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali aur Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Jahash sey bhi ahadees aai hain. aur Abdullah bin Jahash aur unkey betey Muhammad Raziallahu anhuma dono Sahabi Rasool hain."
2798,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' raan bhi sattar (chhipaaney ki chiz) hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2799,"mainey Saeed bin Musaiyab ko kehtey huye suna : Allah pak  hai aur paki (safai aur suthraai) ko pasand karta hai. Allah meharban hai aur meharbani ko pasand karta hai. aur Allah sakhi aur fayyaaz hai aur sakhawat ko pasand karta hai, Tu Pak aur saaf rakho. (mera khayal hai ke unhoney is sey aagey kaha) apney gharon key sehnon aur gharon key samney key maidaanon ko, aur Yahud sey mushaabihat na ikhtiyar karo.'' (saleh kehtey hain) mainey is (riwayat) ka Muhajir bin Mismaar sey zikr kiya to unhoney kaha ke mujh sey is ko Aamir bin Saad ney apney baap Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya. albatta Muhajir ney « نظفوا أفنيتكم » kaha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai.2 - Khalid bin Ilyas zaeef samjhey jatey hain aur unhen Khalid bin Ayas bhi kaha jata hai."
2800,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum log nangey honey sey bacho, kyonkey tumharey sath wo (farishtey) hotey hain jo tum sey juda nahin hotey. wo to sirf us waqt juda hotey hain jab aadmi pakhana jata hai ya apni biwi key paas ja kar us sey hambistar hota hai. isliye tum un ( farishton ( sey sharam khaao aur un ki izzat karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2801,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah par aur qiyamat key din par eman rakhta ho wo tahband baandhey baghair ghusl khaney (hamaam) mein dakhil na ho, jo Allah aur aakhirat key din par eman rakhta ho wo apni biwi ko ghusl khaney ( hamaam ( mein na bhejey , aur jo shakhs Allah par aur aakhirat key din par eman rakhta ho wo aisey dastar khuwan par na bethey jahan sharab ka daur chalta ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf is sanad sey jantey hain. 3- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Les bin abi Sulaim Sadooq hain, lekin kabhi kabhi wo weham kar jatey hain. 4- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : Les ki hadees sey dil khush nahin hota. Les baaz aisi hadeeson ko marfoo bayan kar detey they jisey doosrey log marfoo nahin kartey they. inhen wajuhaat sey logon ney unhen zaeef qarar diya hai."
2802,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mardon aur aurton ko umoomi ghusl khaanon mein ja kar nahaney sey mana farmaya. phir mardon ko tahband pehan kar nahaney ki ijazat deydi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- iski sanad wesi mazbut nahin hai.
2803,ehale teiswin ya ehale Sham ki kuchh aurten ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key paas gaeen to unhoney kaha : tum wohi ho jinki aurten umoomi ghusl khaanon mein nahaney jaya karti hain? mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''jo aurat apney shohar key ghar key siwa apney kapdey kahin dusri jagah utaar kar rakhti hai wo aurat apney aur apney rab key darmiyan sey hijaab ka parda utha deti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2804,"Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein kutta ho, aur na us ghar mein dakhil hotey hain jis mein jandaar mujassmon ki tasweer ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2805,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein khabar di hai : ''farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein mujassamey hon ya tasweer ho.''  (is hadees mein Is-haq Raavi ko shak ho gaya ke unkey ustaad ney « تماثیل » aur « surat » dono mein sey kya kaha ? unhen yad nahin). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2806,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey paas Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney aa kar kaha : ''kal raat main aap key paas aaya tha lekin mujhey aap key paas ghar mein aaney sey is baat ney roka ke aap jis ghar mein they uskey darwazey par mardon ki taswiren thin aur ghar key pardey par bhi taswiren thin. aur ghar mein kutta bhi tha, to aap aisa karen ke darwazey ke (mujassamon) key sar ko udaa dijiye ki wo mujassamey paid jaisey ho jaaeyn, aur pardey phadwaa kar unkey do takiye banwaa dijiye jo padey rahen aur raundey aur istimal kiye jaeyn. aur kuttey ko nikal bhagaaey, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aisa hi kiya. aur wo kutta eik pila tha Hasan ya Husain ka un ki chaarpaai key nichey rehta tha, chunanche aap ney isey bhagaa deney ka hukm diya aur usey bhagaa diya gaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha aur abu-Talha Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2807,eik shakhs surkh rang key do kapdey pehney huye guzraa. usney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko salam kiya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey uskey salam ka jawab nahin diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is hadees sey ehle-ilm key nazdik murad ye hai ke wo zard rang mein ranga huwa kapda pehan'na makrooh samajhtey hain. aur jo kapda gerwey rang waghera mein ranga jaey uskey pehan'ney mein koi muzaaeqa nahin hai jabke wo kusum ka na ho (yani zard rang ka na ho).
2808,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mana farmaya hai) mardon ko) soney ki angoothi pehanney sey , resham miley huye kapdey pehanney sey , zeen par rakhney wali reshmi gaddi sey aur jau ki nabeed sey.Abul Aahwas kehtey hain jau eik sharab hai jo Misr mein jau sey banai jati hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2809,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen saat chizon key ikhtiyar karney ka hukm diya hai aur saat chizon key karney sey mana farmaya hai. aap ney hamein hukm diya hai ke janaazey key sath jaeyn. mareez ki iyaadat karen. chheenkney waley ki chheenk ka jawab den. dawat deney waley ki dawat qubul karen. mazloom ki madad karen. aur qism khaney waley ki qism puri karaein. aur salam ka jawab den. aur saat chizon sey aap ney hamein mana farmaya hai soney ki angoothi pehan'ney, ya soney key chhalley istimal karney sey. aur chaandi key bartanon sey aur hareer , deebaaj , istabraq aur qassi key pehanney sey (ye sab reshmi kapdey hain). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Ash-as bin Sulem : ye Ash-as bin Abu-Sha'shaa hain, Abu-Sha'shaa ka naam Sulem bin Aswad hai."
2810,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''safed kapdey pahno, kyonkey ye pakizah aur umda libas hain, aur unhen safed kapdon ka apney mardon ko kafan do.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2811,"mainey eik intehai roshan chaandni raat mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha , phir aap ko dekhney laga aur chaand ko bhi dekhney laga (ke un dono mein kon ziyada khoobsurat hai) aap us waqt surkh joda pehney huye they, aur aap mujhey chaand sey bhi ziyada Husain nazar aa rahey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Ash-as ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2812,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko do sabz (hara) kapdey istimal kiye huye dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Ubedullah bin yad ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- Abu Ramsa Taimi ka naam Habib bin Hayyan hai aur ye bhi kaha jata hai ke unka naam Rifaa bin Yasribi hai.
2813,"eik subah Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (ghar sey) nikley, us waqt aap kaley baalon ki chadar odhey huye they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
2814,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye phir unhoney puri lambi hadees bayan ki (us mein hai ke) eik shakhs us waqt aaya jab suraj chadh aaya tha. usney kaha : « السلام علیک ya Rasoolullah » ! to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : (وعلیک السلام ورحمة اللہ)‏ ‏‏‏‏ aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (key jism) par do puraney kapdey they. wo za'fraan sey rangey huye they, aur kasrate istimal sey unka rang phika pad gaya tha padhi. aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas khajoor ki eik shaakh thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Qaila ki hadees ko hum sirf Abdullah bin Hassan ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2815,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (mardon ko) za'fraani rang key istimal sey mana farmaya hai, mardon key liye za'fraan key istimal ki karaahat ka matlab ye hai ke mard za'fraan ki khushbu na lagaeyn."
2816,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik shakhs ko khaluq (eik qism ki khshbu jo aurton ke liye khas hai) lagaey huye dekha, to aap ney farmaya : ''jaao isey dho dalo. phir dho dalo, phir (aainda kabhi) na lagaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- baaz logon ney Ata bin Saaib sey is hadees ki snadon mein ikhtilaf kiya hai. 3- Ali (Ali ibne-Madeeni) kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed ney kaha hai ke jisney Ata bin Saaib sey un ki zindagi key puraney (pehley) daur mein suna hai to uska samaa (sun'na), sahih hai aur Shoba aur Sufiyan Sory ka Ata bin Saaib sey samaa (sun'na), sahih hai magar do hadisein jo Ata sey Zazaan key wastey sey marvi (riwayat hui) hain to wo sahih nahin hain. 4- Shoba kehtey hain mainey in dono hadeeson ko Ata sey un ki umr key aakhiri daur mein suna hai. (aur ye hadees un mein sey nahin hai). 5- kaha jata hai ke Ata bin Saaib ka hafiza unkey aakhiri daur mein bigad gaya tha. 6- is bab mein Ammaar, abu-Musa , aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2817,"mainey umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye zikr kartey huye suna hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney duniya mein « hareer » ( reshmi kapda ( pahna to wo usey aakhirat ( yani jannat ( mein na pehnega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Asma bint abi Bakr key azad karda ghulam abu-Amr sey marvi hai. unka naam Abdullah aur un ki kunniyat abu-Amr hai, un sey Ata bin abi Ribah aur Amr bin Dinar ney riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Ali , Huzefa , Anas (Raziallauh anhum) aur deegar kaee logon sey bhi ahadees aai hain, jinka zikr hum kitabul-libas mein kar chukey hain."
2818,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kuch qubaaein taqseem kin , aur Makhrima ko) un mein sey) kuch na diya . Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey merey betey mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ley kar chalo, to main unkey sath gaya. unhoney kaha : tum andar jaao aur aap ko merey paas bula laao, chunanche main aapko unkey paas bula kar laney key liye chala gaya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam nikal kar tashrif laye, to aap key paas un qubaaon mein sey eik qubaa thi'' , aap ney farmaya : '' ye mainey tumharey liye chupa rakhi thi ''. Miswar kehtey hain : phir Makhrima ney aap ko dekha aur bol uthey : Makhrima usey paa kar khush hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ibne-Abi Muleka ka naam Abdullah bin Ubedullah bin abi Muleka hai."
2819,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah apney bandey par apni nemat ka asar dekhna pasand karta hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abul-Ahwas key baap, Imran bin Husain aur ibne-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2820,"Najaashi (Shaahe-Habsha) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko do kalay rang key mozey bhejey, aap ney unhen pahna, phir aap ney wuzu kya aur un dono mozon par masah farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- hum isey sirf Dalham ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 3- Muhammad bin Rabeea ney Dlham ( Raavi ( sey riwayat ki hai."
2821,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney budhapey key (safed) baal ukhedney sey mana kya, aur farmaya hai : ''ye to musalman ka Noor hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Abdur-Rehman bin Haris aur kaee deegar logon sey ye hadees umr bin Shuaib key wastey sey marvi hai."
2822,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Musheer jis sey mashwara liya jata hai us ko amanat daar hona chahiye '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- mutaaddid logon ney Sheban bin Abdur-Rehman Nahwi sey riwayat ki hai, aur Sheban, sahibe-kitab aur sahihul-hadees hain, aur unki kunniyat abu-Muaawia hai, 3- hum sey abdul-Jabbaar bin Alaa Attaar ney bayan kya, unhoney riwayat ki Sufiyan bin Uena sey wo kehtey hain ke abdul-Malik bin Umer ney kaha : jab main hadees bayan karta hun to is hadees ka eik eik lafz ( yani puri hadees ( bayan kar deta hun."
2823,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''musheer yani jis sey mashwara liya jaey us ko ameen hona chahiye''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees hadees Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) ki riwayat sey gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2824,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''nahusat teen chizon mein hai (1) aurat mein (2) ghar mein (3) aur janwer (ghodey) mein '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, 2- Zohri key baaz as-haab (talaamiza) is hadees ka zikr kartey huye « an Hamza» ka zikr nahin kartey balke (عن سالم an أبيه an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) kehtey hain."
2825,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum teen aadmi eik sath ho, to do aadmi apney teesrey sathi ko akela chhod kar baham (aapas mein) kaanaa-phoosi na keren'', Sufiyan ney apni riwayat mein « la يتناجى اثنان دون الثالث فإن ذلك يحزنه » kaha hai, yani '' teesrey shakhs ko chhod kar do sargoshi na karen kyonkey us sey usey dukh aur ranj hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi riwayat ki gaee hai ke aap ney farmaya : '' eik ko nazar andaz kar key do sargoshi na karen, kyonkey us sey momin ko takleef pahunchti hai, aur Allah azz-w-jall momin ki takleef ko pasand nahin karta hai'' , padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2826,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko gora chitta dekha , aap par budhapa aa chala tha Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma ( shakal o surat mein) aap key mushabeh they. aap ney 13 jawan oontniyaan hum ko inayat karney key liye hukm diya, hum unhen leney key liye gaey hi they ke achcha aap key intiqal ki khabar aa gaee, chunanche logon ney hamen kuch na diya, phir jab abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney khilafat ki zimmedaariyan sanbhaalin to unhoney aelan kya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey jis kisi ka bhi koi ehad o paiman ho to wo hamarey paas aaye (aur pesh karey ( chunanche main uth kar unkey paas gaya aur unhen aap key hukm sey aagah kya, to unhoney hamen un oontniyon key deney ka hukm farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Marwan bin Muawiya ney ye hadees apni sanad sey abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, 2- kaee aur logon ney bhi Ismail bin abu-Khalid key wastey sey abu-Juhaifa sey riwayat ki hai, (us riwayat mein hai) wo kehtey hain : mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha hai Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma aap key mushabeh they. aur unhoney us sey ziyada aur kuch nahin kaha."
2827,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha hai, Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma aap key mushabeh they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- isi tarah kaee eik ney Ismail bin abu-Khalid sey isi jaisi riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam Wahab Sawai hai."
2828,mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Saad bin abi Waqas key siwa kisi key liye apney maa baap ko jama kartey huye nahin dekha padhi. .
2829,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney walid aur apni maa ko Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) key siwa kisi key liye jama nahin kya. jange-Uhud mein aap ney un sey kaha : '' teer chalao, tum par merey maa baap qurban hon'', aur aap ney un sey ye bhi kaha : '' aey bahaadur qawi jawan ! teer chalatey jaao ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees Ali sey mutaaddid sanadon sey riwayat ki gaee hai, 3- is hadees ko mutaaddid logon ney Yahya bin Saeed sey, Yahya ney Saeed bin Musaiyab sey , Saeed bin Musaiyab ney Saad bin abi Waqas sey riwayat kya hai. unhoney kaha ahad ki ladaai key din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey liye apney waliden ko yakja kar diya. aap ney farmaya : '' teer chillaey jaao, tum par hamarey maa baap qurban hon'', 4- is bab mein Zuber aur Jabir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2830,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ahad ki ladaai key din merey liye (فداك أبي وأمي) keh kar apney maa baap ko yakjaa kar diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2831,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey (يا بني) '' aey merey betey '' keh kar pukara padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- is sanad key ilawa kuch deegar sanadon sey bhi Anas sey riwayat hai, 3- abu-Usman ye Suqa Shekh hain aur unka naam Jaad bin Usman hai, aur unhen ibn Dinar bhi kaha jata hai aur ye Basra key rehney waley hain. un sey Yunus bin Ubaid aur kaee aimma hadees ney riwayat ki hai, 4- is bab mein Mughira aur umr bin abi Salma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2832,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney saatwen din nau-maulood bachey ka naam rakhney us aur uska aqiqa kar deney ka hukm diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2833,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala key nazdik sab sey ziyada pasandida naam Abdullah aur Abdur-Rehman hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
2834,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala key nazdik sab sey ziyada pasandida naam Abdullah aur Abdur-Rehman hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is sanad sey ye hadees gharib hai.
2835,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ( agar main zinda raha to insha'allah ( Raafey , Barkat aur Yasar naam rakhney sey mana kar dunga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- isi tarah isey abu-Ahmad ney Sufiyan sey abu-Sufiyaan ney abu-Zubair sey abu-Zubair ney Jabir sey aur unhoney umr sey riwayat ki hai. aur abu-Ahmad key ilawa ney Sufiyan sey Sufiyan ney abu-Zubair sey aur abu-Zubair ney Jabir sey Jabir ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, 3- abu-Ahmad Suqa hain Hafiz hain, 4- logon mein ye hadees « an Jabir an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » mashhoor hai aur is hadees mein « an umr » ( umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai) ki sanad sey ka zikr nahin hai."
2836,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum apney ghulam ka naam Ribah, Aflah , Yasar aur najeeh na rakho ( kyonkey ( puchha jaey ke kya wo yahan hai? to kaha jaeyga : nahin '' padhi. ."
2837,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din Allah key nazdik sab sey badtar naam us shakhs ka hoga jis ka naam «malikul-amlak» hoga'' , Sufiyan kehtey hain : «malikul-amlak» ka matlab hai : shahanshaah, aur «akhnaa» key maana «Aqbah» hain yani sab sey badtar aur haqeer tareen . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2838,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney «Aasiya» ka naam badal diya aur kaha ( aaj sey) to « jameela » yani : '' tera naam jameela hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko Yahya bin Saeed Qataan ney marfoo bayan kya hai. Yahya ney Ubedullah sey Ubedullah ney Nafey sey aur Nafey ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ki hai, aur baaz raawiyon ney ye hadees Ubedullah sey, Ubedullah ney Nafey sey aur Nafey ney umr sey mursalan riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin Auf , Abdullah bin Salam, Abdullah bin Mutee, Aaisha, Hakam bin Saeed, Muslim , Usama bin Akhdari, Haani aur Abdur-Rehman bin abi sabra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2839,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bura naam badal diya kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees key Raavi abu-Bakar bin Nafey kehtey hain ke kabhi to umr bin Ali ney is hadees ki sanad mein kaha : (هشام بن عروة an أبيه an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) yani mursalan riwayat ki aur us mein (عن عائشة) key wasta ka zikr nahin kya.
2840,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' merey kaee naam hain : main Muhammad hun, main Ahmed hun, main wo maahi hun jis key zariey Allah kufr ko mitata hai, main wo Haashir hun jiskey qadmon par log jama kiye jaeyngey padhi. main wo aaqib hun jis key baad koi Nabi na paida hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Huzefa sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2841,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mana farmaya hai ke koi shakhs aap ka naam aur aap ki kunniyat dono eik sath jama kar key Muhammad abul-Qaasim naam rakhey padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm makrooh samajhtey hain ke koi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka naam aur aap ki kunniyat eik sath rakhey. lekin baaz logon ney aisa kya hai."
2842,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum merey naam par naam rakho to meri kunniyat na rakho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
2843,unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ka kya khayal hai agar aap key intiqal key baad merey yahan ladka paida ho to kya main uska naam Muhammad aur uski kunniyat aap ki kunniyat par rakh sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : '' haan ''. ( aisa kar saktey ho ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : ye sirf merey liye rukhsat o ijazat thi''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai.
2844,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya: ''baaz ashaar mein hikmat o danai ki baaten hoti hain ''.
2845,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''baaz ashaar mein hikmat o danai ki baaten hoti hain''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2846,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) key liye masjid mein member rakhtey they jis par khadey ho kar wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key liye fakhriya ashaar padhtey they. ya wo apni shaeyri key zariey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka difaa farmatey they. aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farmatey they : ''Allah Hassan ki madad rooh al-qudus ( Jibreel ( key zariey farmata hai jab tak wo (apney ashaar key zariey ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki janib sey fakhr kartey ya aap ka difaa kartey hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. aur ye hadees ibne-Abi Zinad ki riwayat sey hai.
2847,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam umratul-qaza key saal Makka mein dakhil huye aur Abdullah bin Rawaha aap key aagey ye ashaar padhtey huye chal rahey they. (خلوا بني الكفار an سبيله اليوم نضربكم على تنزيله ضربا يزيل الهام an مقيله ويذهل الخليل an خليله) '' aey kuffar ki aulad ! uskey ( yani Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ( raastey sey hat jaao, aaj key din hum tumhen aisi maar maarengey jo khopdi ko gardanon sey juda kar degi, aisi maar maarengey jo dost ko dost sey ghafil kar degi'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney unsey kaha : ibn Rawaha ! tum Rasoolullah key samney aur Allah key Haram mein sher padhtey ho? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : '' unhen kehney do , umr ! ye ashaar un ( kuffar o mushrekin ( par teer barsaney sey bhi ziyada asardaar hain (ye unhen bokhla kar rakh dengey) ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- abdur-Razzaaq ney ye hadees Maamar sey aur Maamar ney Zohri key wastey sey Anas sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, 3- is hadees key ilawa dusri hadees mein marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam umratul-qaza key moqey par Makka mein dakhil huye (us waqt ( Kaab bin Malik aap key sath aap key samney mojud they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : baaz muhaddeseen key nazdik ye ziyada sahih hai isliye ke Abdullah bin Rawaha jang mauta mein maarey gaey hain. aur umratul-qaza uskey baad huwa hai padhi. ."
2848,"un sey puchha gaya : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kabhi koi she'r bator misal aur namoona pesh kartey they? to unhoney kaha : haan , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ibn Rawaha ka sher bator misal pesh kartey they, aap kehtey they : (ويأتيك بالأخبار من لم تزود) Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2849,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''arab ka behtareen sheyree kalam Labid ka ye sher hai : (ألا كل شيء ما خلا الله باطل) '' sun lo ! Allah key siwa har chiz fani hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur usey Sory aur unkey ilawa ney bhi abdul-Malik bin Umer sey riwayat ki hai."
2850,"mujhey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath so baar sey ziyada bethney ka sharf hasil hai, aap key Sahaba sher padhtey ( suntey o sunatey ( they, aur jahiliyat ki bahut si baaten baham (aapas mein) zikr kartey they. aap chup bethey rehtey aur kabhi kabhi unkey sath muskuraney lagtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- usey zuhair bhi ney Samaak sey riwayat kya hai."
2851,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi shakhs key pet ka khoon aalud mawad sey bhar jana jisey wo gala-sada dey , ye kahin behtar hai us sey ke uskey pet ( o seeney ( mein (kufriya shirkiya aur gandey ( ashaar bharey huye hun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad , ibne-Umar , aur Abu-Darda (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2852,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kisi shakhs key pet ka bimari key sabab mawad sey bhar jana behtar hai us sey ke wo she'r sey bhara ho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2853,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala aisey mubaalgha karney waley shakhs ko napasand karta hai jo apni zaban aisey chalata hai jaisey gaey chillati hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2854,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aisi chhat par jahan koi rukawat na ho soney sey mana farmaya hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum is hadees ko sirf Muhammad bin Munkadir ki riwayat sey jantey hain, jisey wo Jabir sey riwayat kartey hain, 3- abdul-jabbaar bin umr zaeef qarar diye gaey hain."
2855,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hum ko waaz o nasihat ka silsiley mein oqaat ka khayal kya kartey they, is dar sey ke kahin hum par uktaahat taari na ho jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2856,ummul-momenin Aaisha aur Umme-Salma Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha gaya ke kon sa amal Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko bahut ziyada pasand tha? un dono ney jawab diya ke wo amal jo bhale hi thoda ho lekin usey mustaqil aur barabar kya jaey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
2857,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' (raat mein) bartanon ko dhanp kar rakho aur mushkon key munh baandh diya karo, ghar key darwazey band kar diya karo, aur chiraghon ko bujha diya karo kyonkey kabhi aisa hota hai ke chuhiyaa chiragh ki batti khinch ley jati hai aur ghar walon ko jala daalti hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees mutaaddid sanadon sey Jabir sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki gaee hai."
2858,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum hariyali aur shadabi key zamaney mein safar karo to oont ko zamin sey uska haq do (yani ji bhar kar char leney diya karo) aur jab tum khizan o khushki aur qehat key dino mein safar karo uski quwat sey faeyda utha leney mein karo to jaldi padhi. aur jab tum raat mein qiyam key liye padaaw dalo to aam raastey sey hat kar qiyam karo, kyonkey ye ( raastey (raat mein chopayon key raastey aur keedon makodon key thikaney hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
